OL,3,CThousands of Bolton Wanderers' fans
OL,4,Ccelebrate promotion
OL,6,FThousands of Bolton Wanderers' fans
OL,7,Fgathered to celebrate their club's
OL,8,Fpromotion to the Championship.
OL,10,FPlayers and coaching staff marked the
OL,11,Fhistoric occasion with a civic
OL,12,Freception at Bolton Town Hall after
OL,13,Ftheir 4-1 victory over local rivals
OL,14,FStockport County in the League One
OL,15,FPlay-Off Final at Wembley on 23 May.
OL,17,FPlayers were greeted on a scorching
OL,18,Fbank holiday Monday by generations of
OL,19,Fsupporters who have waited seven years
OL,20,Fto see their club back into the second
OL,21,Ftier.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
