OL,3,CThousands of Bolton Wanderers' fans
OL,4,Ccelebrate promotion
OL,6,FFans set off blue and white flares and
OL,7,Fand sang the name of manager Steven
OL,8,FSchumacher as the team showed off
OL,9,Ftheir silverware.
OL,11,F"It's been a brilliant weekend,"
OL,12,FSteven said. "It is a weekend we could
OL,13,Fhave only dreamed of but the
OL,14,Fperformance we put on and the
OL,15,Fcelebrations after have been
OL,16,Foutstanding."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
