FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779815153
OL,3,CThousands of Bolton Wanderers' fans
OL,4,Ccelebrate promotion
OL,6,FSchumacher saw Ruben Rodrigues start
OL,7,Fand finish the scoring in a 4-1 League
OL,8,FOne play-off final victory to secure
OL,9,Fthe club's second-tier status. Second-
OL,10,Fhalf substitute Sam Dalby, and a Kyle
OL,11,FWootton own goal, completed the rout.
OL,13,F"To see our fans celebrate at the end
OL,14,Flike that was nothing more than what
OL,15,Fthey deserve," Steven added. "The
OL,16,Freception today has been outstanding.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
