PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779815153
OL,3,CThousands of Bolton Wanderers' fans
OL,4,Ccelebrate promotion
OL,6,F"This football club means so much to
OL,7,Fthe town and everyone that has
OL,8,Fsupported us week in and week out,
OL,9,Fespecially away from home, it has been
OL,10,Fincredible."
OL,12,FThe Trotters manager is now looking
OL,13,Fahead to a busy summer because there
OL,14,F"is lots of work to do".
OL,16,F"We're going into a higher level that
OL,17,Fis really competitive but one that we
OL,18,Fshould be prepared for," he said. "I'm
OL,19,Fready to accept the challenge."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
