OL,3,CThousands of Bolton Wanderers' fans
OL,4,Ccelebrate promotion
OL,6,FAhead of the civic reception, Sharon
OL,7,FBrittan, Chairman of Bolton Wanderers
OL,8,FFootball Club, said: "We are
OL,9,Fincredibly proud to have secured
OL,10,Fpromotion and to bring this success
OL,11,Fback to Bolton.
OL,13,F"The support from the town and our
OL,14,Ffans has been unwavering, and this
OL,15,Fachievement belongs to everyone
OL,16,Fconnected to the club.
OL,18,F"We are grateful to Bolton Council for
OL,19,Fhosting this civic reception and look
OL,20,Fforward to celebrating together with
OL,21,Fthe community."
